              },
              "blocks": {
                "accordion_row_ptGKfD": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How Will My Appointment Work?",
                    "open_by_default": true,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_3Wa7VF": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Your MWL appointment offers complete privacy, with the entire studio reserved just for you. Explore our entire <a href=\"https://madewithlovebridal.com/collections/made-to-order\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://madewithlovebridal.com/collections/made-to-order\">made to order collection</a> with the help of one of our dedicated bridal stylists, who will assist with everything from styling to fit. You will be welcomed with a glass of bubbles as one of our expert stylists guide you through finding the perfect dress to match your wedding style and body shape. We recommend trying 4 - 6 dresses.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_3Wa7VF"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_LBAC3D": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Before Your Appointment",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_WTH7Ln": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>It is best to do some research to determine which designs you hope to try on. It can also be helpful to bring undergarments of similar styles that you will wear on your wedding day. We recommend nude undergarments where possible.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_WTH7Ln"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_W8VhGJ": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How Many Guests Are Allowed In Appointments?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_xec4dm": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>We recommend 1-4 guests per bride in our bridal boutiques. You are welcome to video call any family and friends who can’t be with you on the day. Unfortunately, we do not allow children, but babies in prams are welcome.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_xec4dm"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_7fKfWm": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "How Does Sizing Work?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_d6rn8r": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>During your appointment, our trained stylists will help you choose the best size based on your measurements. When you are ready to place your order, your stylist will record your agreed size within your file. Please note: we offer split sizing if your bust, waist, and hip measurements don’t align with a single standard size.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
