                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_d6rn8r"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_ir8M8i": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "What Are Sample Sizes?",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_xj9yB4": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Our in boutique sample dresses are available in sizes 6 to 18. We also carry a small selection of styles in sizes outside this range, and do our best to accommodate a variety of body types. If you have any size specific questions, please reach out to our customer care team.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_xj9yB4"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_jhYHhp": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Fittings And Alterations",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_rwxTf3": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Our dresses are made to the closest standard size based on your measurements, so some alterations are usually needed for the perfect fit. We consider your height and heel height, but you may want to adjust length or straps. We can recommend trusted local seamstresses and suggest budgeting for alterations. Second fittings aren’t offered since we match your measurements to our size chart.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_rwxTf3"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_qpEajy": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "When To Place Orders",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_NPUkBb": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>We offer standard and priority order options based on how far your order is from your wedding date. To ensure the right timing, please discuss your timeline with your stylist during your appointment. The earlier you place your order, the smoother the process.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
                        "letter_spacing": "normal",
                        "case": "none",
                        "wrap": "pretty",
                        "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                        "background": false,
                        "background_color": "#00000026",
                        "corner_radius": 0,
                        "padding-block-start": 0,
                        "padding-block-end": 0,
                        "padding-inline-start": 0,
                        "padding-inline-end": 0
                      },
                      "blocks": {}
                    }
                  },
                  "block_order": [
                    "text_NPUkBb"
                  ]
                },
                "accordion_row_wUKBgU": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Photo Policy",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_jYymRw": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Although we allow photos, we request that you wait until the end of your appointment when you have narrowed down your selection to 1 or 2 dresses.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "enable_mobile_size": false,
                        "mobile_font_size": "1rem",
                        "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                        "font_size": "0.75rem",
                        "line_height": "normal",
